flowchart LR
  Value[User gets useful output] --> Save[Output saved to Vault]
  Save --> Proof[Proof improves trust]
  Proof --> Deploy[Deploy agent / workflow / portal]
  Deploy --> Usage[More usage]
  Usage --> Limit[Hits plan or credit limit]
  Limit --> Upgrade[Upgrade / top-up / Business Space]
  Upgrade --> Revenue[Revenue funds better AI and templates]
  Revenue --> Better[Better agents, spaces, and marketplace]
  Better --> Value
